<doc id='bbc_51871911' type='mono' source_url='https://www.bbc.co.uk/gahuza/51871911' term='COVID'>
Coronavirus: Premier League yahagaritswe

Premier League imaze gutangaza ko inama y'abagize iri rushanwa ry'umupira w'amaguru mu Bwongereza yemeje guhagarika iri rushanwa kubera inama z'abaganga n'uko ibintu byifashe ubu.
Icyorezo cya coronavirus gikomeje gutuma hahagarikwa ibikorwa binyuranye bihuriramo abantu benshi ku isi, birinda ikwirakwira ryayo.
Premier League yatangaje ko ku bwumvikane n'ishyirahamwe ry'umupira w'amaguru mu Bwongereza (FA) hanahagaritswe andi marushanwa.
Ayo ni; English Football League Championship, FA Women's Super League ndetse na FA Cup.
Itangazo basohoye rivuga ko icyifuzo ari uko imikino ya Premier League yasubukurwa tariki 04 z'ukwezi gutaha kwa kane.
Richard Masters uyobora Premier League yavuze ko "hejuru ya byose, twifuriza Mikel Arteta na Callum Hudson-Odoi gukira vuba, n'abandi bose bagezweho na Covid-19".
Callum Hudson-Odoi ni umukinnyi wa Chelsea FC nawe basanzemo iyi ndwara, kimwe na Arteta umutoza mukuru wa Arsenal.
Premier League ivuga ko izamenyesha amakuru mashya mu gihe nyacyo ku mikino y'iri rushanwa rifatwa nk'irya mbere rikunzwe cyane ku isi mu mupira w'amaguru.
Amarushanwa y'umupira w'amaguru mu Butaliyani na Espagne nayo yamaze guhagarikwa kubera iki cyorezo.Imikino yari iteganyijwe ejo kuwa gatandatu no ku cyumweru ntikibaye
