Coronavirus: Abanduye biyongereye, u Rwanda rwafashe izindi ngamba
Mu minsi itanu ishize abanduye Covid-19 mu Rwanda bavuye kuri 1 bagera kuri 11, leta y'u Rwanda ubu yatangaje ihagarikwa ry'ingendo z'indege - harimo n'iza kompanyi ya leta Rwandair - ziva cyangwa zijya mu Rwanda kuva uyu munsi ku wa kane saa sita z'ijoro.
Mu minsi itanu ishize abanduye Covid-19 mu Rwanda bavuye kuri 1 bagera kuri 11, leta y'u Rwanda ubu yatangaje ihagarikwa ry'ingendo z'indege - harimo n'iza kompanyi ya leta Rwandair - ziva cyangwa zijya mu Rwanda kuva uyu munsi ku wa kane saa sita z'ijoro.
Muri 11 banduye virus ya Covid-19 mu Rwanda babiri ni bo badaheruka mu mahanga, kimwe n'ahandi henshi muri Afurika iyi ndwara imaze cyane cyane kuboneka ku bavuye mu mahanga.
Iki cyemezo kizamara iminsi 30, cyagize u Rwanda igihugu cya mbere mu karere gihagaritse ingendo zose z'indege zitwara abantu ziva cyangwa ziza mu gihugu kubera iyi ndwara.
Minisiteri y'ubuzima mu Rwanda ariko yavuze ko indege z'ubwikorezi bw'ibintu (cargo) zo zizakomeza ingendo zazo mu Rwanda.
Ibindi bihugu binyuranye byo byatangaje ko bihagaritse ingendo z'indege ziva cyangwa zijya mu bihugu bimaze kugeramo iyi ndwara.
Gusa kugeza ubu ibihugu 176 ku isi, na 32 muri 54 bya Afurika bimaze kugeramo iyi ndwara, bisobanuye ko ingendo z'indege ziri kugenda zihagarikwa hose.
Ihagarikwa ry'ingendo z'indege mu Rwanda ni icyemezo gifite ingaruka ku bikorwa by'abantu bwite n'ubukungu muri rusange, gusa ni icyemezo bamwe bagaragaje ko gikwiye muri ibi bihe.
Kompanyi z'indege nka Brussels Airlines, KLM, Kenya Airways, Jambo Jet, Qatar Airways, Ethiopian Airlines n'izindi, zisanzwe zigwa zikanahaguruka mu Rwanda buri munsi.
Brussels Airlines yari iherutse gutangaza ko izakora urugendo rwayo rwa nyuma i Kigali uyu munsi tariki 19/03/2020 igasubika izindi kugeza mu kwa kane, mu kwirinda ikwirakwira ry'iyi ndwara.
Banki nkuru mu Rwanda yasohoye itangazo rikubiyemo amabwiriza yo koroshya ingaruka za Covid-19, muri yo harimo:
Mu Rwanda, iyi ndwara yasubitse inama mpuzamahanga zigera kuri 20 zari kwinjiza mu bukungu bw'iki gihugu imari igera kuri miliyoni $8 nk'uko biherutse gutangazwa n'ikigo gishinzwe ibi bikorwa.
Coronavirus imaze gutuma hari abantu ku giti cyabo basubika bimwe mu bihuza abantu benshi, nk'ubukwe, byari bibeshejeho abantu bamwe bakura amafaranga mu gutanga serivisi.
</doc>
<doc id='bbc_amakuru-51960775' type='mono' source_url='https://www.bbc.co.uk/gahuza/amakuru-51960775' term='COVID'>
Coronavirus: Trump avuga ko ubu Amerika iri mu ntambara n'iki cyorezo
Yiyita "perezida wo mu ntambara", Perezida Donald Trump yasezeranyije ko Leta Zunze Ubumwe z'Amerika zizagera ku "ntsinzi yuzuye" mu ntambara zirimo kurwana na coronavirus.
Yiyita "perezida wo mu ntambara", Perezida Donald Trump yasezeranyije ko Leta Zunze Ubumwe z'Amerika zizagera ku "ntsinzi yuzuye" mu ntambara zirimo kurwana na coronavirus.
Yabivuze ubwo yasubizagaho ingamba yo mu gihe cy'intambara yo muri Koreya yemerera Amerika kongera ikorwa ry'ibikoresho by'ingenzi mu buvuzi.
Hagati aho, abadepite babiri ejo ku wa gatatu babaye aba mbere mu bagize inteko ishingamategeko y'Amerika banduye coronavirus.
Abo ni Ben McAdams, umudemokarate uhagarariye leta ya Utah, na Mario Diaz-Balart, umurepubulikani uhagarariye leta ya Florida.
Muri Amerika abantu barenga 9,300 bamaze kwandura Covid-19 - indwara yo mu myanya y'ubuhumekero iterwa n'iyo virusi -  naho abagera 150 imaze kubica.
Ku isi, abantu barenga 220,000 bemejwe ko bayanduye kugeza ubu. Abarenga  8,800 imaze kubica.
Mu kiganiro n'abanyamakuru mu biro bye bya White House, Perezida Trump yabajijwe n'umunyamakuru niba abifata nkaho iki gihugu kiri mu gihe nk'icy'intambara mu rwego rwo kurwanya iyo virusi.
Yasubije ati: "Ni intambara. Mbifata, urebye, nkaho ndi perezida wo mu ntambara".
Muri iki cyumweru, Bwana Trump yakoresheje ibiganiro bya buri munsi kuri ibi bihe bidasanzwe igihugu kirimo, nyuma yaho ashinjwe kuba yarirengagije coronavirus mu bihe bya mbere byayo muri Amerika.
Yagize ati: "Tugomba kwigomwa twese hamwe, kubera ko iki kibazo twese turagifatanyije, kandi tuzakirangiriza hamwe. Ni umwanzi utaboneshwa amaso. Uwo iteka ahora ari we mwanzi ukomeye cyane [kurwanya]".
"Ariko tugiye gutsinda uyu mwanzi utaboneshwa amaso. Ntekereza ko tugiye no kumutsinda byihuse kurusha uko twabitekerezaga, kandi izaba ari intsinzi yuzuye..."
Bwana Trump yatangaje ko agiye gushyira umukono ku itegeko-teka rizwi nka '1950 Defense Production Act', riha ububasha perezida gutegeka ibikorwa by'ubucuruzi by'abasivile gufasha mu gukora ibicyenewe ku bw'inyungu z'umutekano w'igihugu.
Ariko nyuma yatangaje ku rubuga rwa Twitter ko yafata iyo ngamba gusa "ibintu bigeze irudubi mu gihe kiri imbere".
Bwana Trump yanavuze ku magambo ya Steve Mnuchin, umukuru w'ibiro by'imari by'Amerika, yuko iki cyorezo gishobora gutuma ubushomeri bwiyongera bikomeye bukagera ku 20%.
Avuga kuri ayo magambo ya Bwana Mnuchin, Perezida Trump yavuze ko ibyo byaba ari uko "ibintu byageze irudubi burundu burundu".
Perezida Trump kandi yavuze ko ibitaro  byo mu bwato bubiri bw'abasirikare barwanira mu mazi bizakoreshwa mu gufasha kugabanya umuzigo witezwe kubaho kubera ukudahaza kw'ibitanda by'abarwayi.
Byitezwe ko ubwato buzwi nka 'USNS Comfort' bwoherezwa ku mwaro wa New York Harbor, nubwo abategetsi bo mu rwego rwa gisirikare bavuze ko kuri ubu buri gukorerwa isuzuma ry'imikorere muri leta ya Virginia.
Ubundi bwato, buzwi nka 'USNS Mercy', buri gutegurirwa koherezwa mu burengerazuba bw'Amerika.
Muri icyo kiganiro n'abanyamakuru cyo ku munsi w'ejo ku wa gatatu, Bwana Trump yongeye guhakana ibivugwa ko ugukoresha kwe kw'ijambo "virusi y'Ubushinwa" ashaka kuvuga Covid-19, kurimo ivangurabwoko.
Mbere yaho kuri uwo munsi, umupaka ugabanya Amerika na Canada, wa mbere mu burebure ku isi, urebye warafunzwe, usibye gusa ku ngendo z'ingenzi no ku bucuruzi.
Bwana Trump yanatangaje ingamba nshya yo guhashya abimukira n'abashaka ubuhungiro bambuka umupaka w'Amerika na Mexico.
Yavuze ko ubutegetsi bwe buzifashisha itegeko rituma abantu bakumirwa mu kwirinda ikwirakwira ry'indwara zandura.
</doc>
<doc id='bbc_51971863' type='mono' source_url='https://www.bbc.co.uk/gahuza/51971863' term='COVID'>
Coronavirus: “Dufite ikizere ko Imana izaturinda” – Karerwa umuvugizi wa Perezida Nkurunziza
Mu Burundi ubuzima bukomeje nk'uko bisanzwe, umuvugizi w'umukuru w'igihugu Jean Claude Karerwa Ndenzako avuga ko iki gihugu cyahaye Imana umwanya udasanzwe bityo bizeye ko izakomeza kubarinda iki cyorezo, nubwo ngo biteguye kukirwanya kihageze.
Mu Burundi ubuzima bukomeje nk'uko bisanzwe, umuvugizi w'umukuru w'igihugu Jean Claude Karerwa Ndenzako avuga ko iki gihugu cyahaye Imana umwanya udasanzwe bityo bizeye ko izakomeza kubarinda iki cyorezo, nubwo ngo biteguye kukirwanya kihageze.
Nta murwayi wa Covid-19 uraboneka mu Burundi nk'uko abategetsi babitangaza, kugeza ubu iyi ndwara imaze kugera mu bihugu 33 muri 54 bya Afurika.
Ishami rya UN rishinzwe ubuzima ku isi OMS/WHO rigaragaza muri aka karere u Rwanda, Kenya, DR Congo na Tanzania ariho iyi ndwara imaze kugera, bitatu muri ibi bihugu ni ibituranyi n'u Burundi.
Aho iyi ndwara imaze kugera bahagaritse amashuri, amakoraniro y'abasenga, ingendo nyinshi z'indege, inama zihuza abantu benshi banashishikariza abantu kwirinda guhurira ahari abantu benshi.
Bwana Karerwa avuga ko mu Burundi ingamba zafashwe mu kwirinda iyi ndwara zigendanye no kuba iyi virus itarahagera.
Yabwiye BBC ati: "Izindi zizafatwa mu gihe bizagaragara ko koko icyo kiza kibangamiye igihugu ku rugero ibindi bihugu nk'Ubutaliyano n'Ubushinwa cyangwa ibyo by'Iburayi bigezeho.
"Ingingo ubu zafashwe ni izo kuzitira tutaronerwa, [ariko] uko umuntu yonerwa niko afata izindi ngingo nshyashya".
Mu burundi, ibikorwa bihuza abantu benshi, imyidagaduro, imikino, amaterani y'abasenga birakomeje nubwo ngo ababijyamo basabwa kwisunga ingingo nko gukaraba intoki, kwirinda kuramukanya, kwirinda kwegerana n'ibindi.
Bwana Karerwa ati"Ni ingingo zidasanzwe, abantu nubwo bahura ntibifata nk'uko bari basanzwe, biraboneka ko hari ikintu cyahindutse mu kubaho kw'abantu no mu mahuriro bahuriramo".
Bwana Karerwa avuga ko bizeye ko iyi ndwara nubwo yagera mu Burundi bizera ko itageza mu kwezi kwa gatanu ngo ibangamire amatora y'umukuru w'igihugu ateganyijwe tariki 20/05/2020.
Abajijwe niba bidashoboka ko iyi ndwara ishobora kubangamira amatora yagize ati:
"Byabangamira amatora mu gihe cyaba cyabaye ikiza cyakwiye igihugu cyose hafashwe ingingo nka ziriya zifatwa igihugu kiri mu ntambara".
Bwana Karerwa avuga ko u Burundi ari igihugu cyahaye Imana umwanya wa mbere, ko bizeye ko iyo Mana izaza ikabarinda ibyago byose.
Ati: "Ibyago byarateye hirya no hino ku isi ariko bigaca inyuma y'u Burundi, n'ubu rero dufite ukwizera ko ubu bwo kuko Imana twayihaye umwanya udasanzwe izaza nayo iturinde ibyo byose mwibaza ko bishobora gushyika".
Gusa avuga ko Imana nayo ngo isaba abantu kuba abanyabwenge ariyo mpamvu nabo biteguye bigendanye n'uko mu gihugu ubu bimeze.
