Coronavirus: Abanduye ku munsi muri Koreya y'Epfo bageze ku kigero cyo hejuru kitaribwabeho mbere
Koreya y'Epfo yagize umubare munini wa mbere w'abanduye coronavirus ku munsi umwe, ubwo byemezwaga ko abantu 594 bashya ari bo banduye ubu bwoko bushya bw'iyi virusi ejo ku wa gatanu.
Koreya y'Epfo yagize umubare munini wa mbere w'abanduye coronavirus ku munsi umwe, ubwo byemezwaga ko abantu 594 bashya ari bo banduye ubu bwoko bushya bw'iyi virusi ejo ku wa gatanu.
Uko kwiyongera gutumye umubare wose w'abamaze kuyandura muri Koreya y'Epfo bagera ku 2,931, nkuko bitangazwa n'ikigo cy'iki gihugu gishinzwe kurwanya no kwirinda indwara.
Abantu 17 ni bo bamaze gupfa bishwe na coronavirus muri iki gihugu kugeza ubu.
Koreya y'Epfo ni yo ifite umubare munini w'abemejwe ko banduye coronavirus bo hanze y'Ubushinwa - igihugu ubu bwoko bushya bw'iyi virusi bwatangiriyemo mu kwezi kwa cumi na kabiri mu mwaka ushize.
Mu yandi makuru, hari impungenge ku mubare w'abantu bashya banduye batazwi aho bayikomoye bo muri Leta Zunze Ubumwe z'Amerika muri leta za California na Oregon.
Benshi muri abo bantu bashya banduye Covid-19 - indwara yo mu myanya y'ubuhumekero iterwa n'ubu bwoko bushya bwa coronavirus - bo muri Koreya y'Epfo ni abo mu mujyi wa Daegu, mu majyepfo ashyira uburasirazuba bw'igihugu.
Uwo mujyi ni wo wabaye izingiro rya coronavirus muri iki gihugu.
Gukwirakwira kwa coronavirus muri Koreya y'Epfo gufitanye isano n'umuryango wa gikristu wo mu itorero rya Shincheonji.
Abategetsi bemeza ko abo muri iryo torero bagiye banduzanya mu masengesho i Daegu nuko bakanduza n'abandi mu gihugu, nta muntu ubitahuye.
Ayo makuru mashya kuri coronavirus aje mu gihe ku munsi w'ejo ku wa gatanu ishami ry'umuryango w'abibumbye ryita ku buzima (OMS/WHO) ryongereye ikigero cyaryo cy'ibyago bitewe na coronavirus kikajya ku cyo hejuru hashoboka.
Ariko OMS yavuze ko hakiri amahirwe yo guhagarika coronavirus mu gihe haba hashenywe uruhererekane rw'uko yandura.
Dr Tedros Adhanom Ghebreyesus, umukuru wa OMS, yanashimangiye ko ubwoba n'ikwirakwira ry'amakuru ayobya biri mu ngorane zikomeye cyane zo guhangana nazo.
</doc>
<doc id='bbc_amakuru-51614265' type='mono' source_url='https://www.bbc.co.uk/gahuza/amakuru-51614265' term='COVID'>
Coronavirus: Gukwirakwira kwihuse kwateje ubwoba ko ishobora kugera ku rwego rw'icyorezo
Ubwoba buri kwiyongera ko coronavirus ishobora kugera ku rwego rw'icyorezo mu gihe hakomeje kugaragara abandi bantu mu bice bitandukanye by'isi bayirwaye.
Ubwoba buri kwiyongera ko coronavirus ishobora kugera ku rwego rw'icyorezo mu gihe hakomeje kugaragara abandi bantu mu bice bitandukanye by'isi bayirwaye.
Benshi mu bayanduye ni abo mu Bushinwa, ariko ibindi bihugu nka Koreya y'Epfo, Ubutaliyani na Iran bihanganye n'ubwo bwoko bushya bw'iyo virusi itera indwara yo mu myanya y'ubuhumekero yitwa Covid-19.
Bivugwa ko indwara yabaye icyorezo iyo yandura ikwirakwiriye mu buryo bworoshye iva ku muntu umwe ijya ku wundi mu bice byinshi by'isi.
Abantu hafi  77,000 bo mu Bushinwa, aho iyo virusi yagaragaye mu mwaka ushize, bamaze kuyandura ndetse abandi hafi 2,600 imaze kubica.
Abantu barenga 1,200 bamaze kwemezwa ko bayanduye mu bindi bihugu hafi 30 naho abantu barenga 20 imaze kubahitana. Kuri uyu wa mbere, Ubutaliyani bwatangaje ko abandi bantu babiri yabishe, bituma umubare w'abo imaze kwica muri iki gihugu ugera kuri batanu.
Ikigero cy'abarwayi bayirwaye bari gupfa kubera iyo ndwara izwi nka Covid-19 kigaragara nk'ikiri hagati ya 1% na 2%, nubwo ishami ry'umuryango w'abimbumbye ryita ku buzima (OMS/WHO) riburira ko ikigero cy'abo yica kitaramenyekana.
Kuri uyu wa mbere, Iraq, Afghanistan, Kuwait na Bahrain byatangaje abantu ba mbere byemeje ko bayirwaye, bose bahageze bavuye muri Iran.
Tedros Adhanom Ghebreyesus, umukuru wa OMS, yari yaburiye ko igihe cy'amahirwe yo guhagarika coronavirus "kiri kugabanuka".
Paul Hunter, wigisha kwirinda mu bijyanye n'ubuzima bw'abantu kuri Kaminuza ya East Anglia mu Bwongereza, yunze mu ry'umukuru wa OMS, avuga ko kwiyongera kw'abarwayi ba coronavirus mu Bushinwa "biteye impungenge zikomeye".
Kuri uyu wa mbere, Bwana Hunter yagize ati: "Igihe aho nyuma yacyo nta garuriro mu bushobozi bwacu bwo kurinda ko iba icyorezo ku isi, gisa nkaho cyarushijeho kutwegera nyuma y'amasaha 24 ashize".
Margaret Harris, umuvugizi wa OMS, yabwiye BBC ko uko ibintu bimeze ubu bitari kubonwa nk'icyorezo kuko ibihugu bigishobora kurinda ko iyo virusi ikwirakwira byihuse cyane.
Ati: "Iyo ibihugu biramuka nta ngamba na busa byafashe, twari kuba twarabonye abantu benshi cyane kurushaho bayanduye. Icyo ni cyo tuba dushatse kuvuga iyo tuvuze guhagarika".
