<doc id='bbc_amakuru-51542097' type='mono' source_url='https://www.bbc.co.uk/gahuza/amakuru-51542097' term='COVID'>
Coronavirus: Ubushakashatsi bushya bw'Ubushinwa bugaragaza ko abakuze bari mu bo yibasira
Abategetsi bo mu rwego rw'ubuzima mu Bushinwa batangaje amakuru ya mbere ajyanye n'abantu barenga 44,000 barwaye indwara ya Covid-19 iterwa n'ubwoko bushya bwa coronavirus, mu bushakashatsi bwa mbere bwimbitse bubayeho kuva iyo virusi yatangira.
Abategetsi bo mu rwego rw'ubuzima mu Bushinwa batangaje amakuru ya mbere ajyanye n'abantu barenga 44,000 barwaye indwara ya Covid-19 iterwa n'ubwoko bushya bwa coronavirus, mu bushakashatsi bwa mbere bwimbitse bubayeho kuva iyo virusi yatangira.
Ayo makuru y'abarwayi y'ikigo cy'Ubushinwa cyo guhangana no kurinda indwara (Chinese Centre for Disease Control and Prevention, CCDC), yasanze abarenga 80% by'abayirwaye bayirwaye byoroheje, mu gihe abasanzwe barwaye n'abageze mu zabukuru - b'imyaka 80 kuzamura - ari bo yibasira kurusha abandi.
Ubwo bushakashatsi bunavuga ko abaganga bari mu bafite ibyago byinshi byo kuyandura.
Butangajwe mu gihe kuri uyu wa kabiri umukuru w'ibitaro mu mujyi wa Wuhan yishwe n'iyo virusi.
Liu Zhiming w'imyaka 51 y'amavuko yari umukuru w'ibitaro bya Wuchang Hospital by'i Wuhan - bimwe mu bikora akazi gakomeye mu guhangana n'iyo virusi muri ako gace gafatwa nk'izingiro ryayo.
Bwana Zhiming ni umwe mu baganga bo ku rwego rwo hejuru bamaze kwicwa na Covid-19.
Hubei, intara irimo uwo mujyi wa Wuhan, ni yo yashegeshwe cyane n'iyo virusi kurusha ahandi hose mu Bushinwa.
Ubwo bushakashatsi bw'ikigo CCDC bugaragaza ko ikigero cy'abo ihitana mu ntara ya Hubei kiri kuri 2.9% mu gihe ahandi mu gihugu kiri gusa kuri 0.4%.
Muri rusange, ubwo bushakashatsi buvuga ko ikigero cy'abicwa na Covid-19 kiri kuri 2.3%.
Imibare mishya yasohowe kuri uyu wa kabiri na leta y'Ubushinwa igaragaza ko muri rusange Covid-19 imaze kwica abantu 1,868 naho abandi 72,436 bakaba bamaze kuyandura muri iki gihugu.
Abategetsi bavuze ko abantu 98 bashya ari bo yishe naho abandi 1,886 bakayandura ku munsi wabanje, 93 muri abo bashya yishe na 1,807 bayanduye bakaba ari abo mu ntara ya Hubei.
Abantu barenga 12,000 bamaze kuyikira, nkuko abategetsi bo mu Bushinwa babivuga.
Ubwo bushakashatsi bw'ikigo CCDC bwasohotse ejo ku wa mbere, bwanatangajwe mu kinyamakuru cy'ubushakashatsi ku bitera indwara cyo mu Bushinwa cya 'Chinese Journal of Epidemiology'.
Bwibanze ku bantu barenga 44,000 basanganwe Covid-19 mu Bushinwa kugeza ku itariki ya 11 y'uku kwezi kwa kabiri, barimo abemejwe ko bayanduye, abacyekwa ko bayanduye ndetse n'abadahita bagaragaza ibimenyetso byayo.
</doc>
<doc id='bbc_amakuru-51557897' type='mono' source_url='https://www.bbc.co.uk/gahuza/amakuru-51557897' term='COVID'>
Coronavirus: Abagenzi bakuwe mu bwato Diamond Princess mu Buyapani
Abagenzi ba mbere babarirwa mu magana basanzwe nta bwoko bushya bwa coronavirus barwaye, batangiye kuva mu bwato buparitse ku cyambu mu Buyapani, nyuma yo kumara iminsi 14 mu kato.
Abagenzi ba mbere babarirwa mu magana basanzwe nta bwoko bushya bwa coronavirus barwaye, batangiye kuva mu bwato buparitse ku cyambu mu Buyapani, nyuma yo kumara iminsi 14 mu kato.
Abagera kuri 542 mu bagenzi n'abakozi bo mu bwato Diamond Princess banduye iyi virusi izwi nka Covid-19 - ni bo benshi bamaze kuyandura bo hanze y'Ubushinwa.
Abagenzi bavuze ukuntu babaye mu buzima bugoye bwo gushyirwa mu kato muri ubwo bwato kuva mu ntangiriro y'uku kwezi kwa kabiri.
Ibihugu byinshi biri guhungisha abaturage babyo bari muri ubwo bwato, mu gihe umubare w'abandura ukomeza kwiyongera.
Ku cyumweru, Leta Zunze Ubumwe z'Amerika zakuye muri ubwo bwato abaturage babwo babarirwa muri za magana, zibashyira mu kato.
Ubwongereza bwavuze ko bwizeye "muri iki cyumweru" gushyira mu ndege bugatahura abaturage babwo 74 bari mu bwato Diamond Princess.
Umugore n'umugabo bakomoka mu Bwongereza bari muri ubwo bwato - bamaze igihe baha amakuru abanyamakuru ndetse banayatangaza ku mbuga nkoranyambaga k'ukuntu ibintu bimeze mu bwato - bemeje kuri uyu wa gatatu ko bapimwe bagasanga baranduye iyo virusi.
Amerika, Canada, Australia n'Ubwongereza bizashyira abakuwe muri ubwo bwato mu kandi kato k'iminsi 14 ubwo bazaba bageze iwabo.
Covid-19  - nkuko indwara iterwa n'ubu bwoko bushya bwa coronavirus yitwa - ubu imaze kwica abantu 2,004 mu Bushinwa, nkuko bikubiye mu mibare mishya ya leta yatangajwe kuri uyu wa gatatu.
Abantu 74,185 bamaze kwemezwa ko bayirwaye mu Bushinwa, n'abandi bagera hafi kuri 700 bayirwaye mu bindi bihugu.
Kuri uyu wa gatatu Hong Kong yatangaje ko umugabo w'imyaka 70 wari urwaye n'izindi ndwara yabaye umuntu wa kabiri yishe aha muri Hong Kong. Ubufaransa, Ubuyapani, Philippines na Taiwan, buri hamwe hapfuye umuntu yishwe n'iyo virusi.
Ku wa mbere, Ubushinwa bwatangaje ubushakashatsi bwakorewe ku barenga 44,000 bemejwe ko barwaye iyo virusi, bwagaragaje ko umubare munini w'abo yica baba ari abasanzwe barwaye izindi ndwara n'abageze mu zabukuru.
Hafi abantu 500 basanzwe badafite iyo virusi kandi bakaba nta kimenyetso na kimwe cyayo bagaragaza, bitezwe  kuva mu bwato Diamond Princess buri ku cyambu cya Yokohama kuri uyu wa gatatu, abandi bakazabuvamo mu minsi iri imbere.
Ubwo bwato bwari butwaye abantu 3,700 bose hamwe.
Umunyamakuru wa BBC Laura Bicker uri ku cyambu cya Yokohama avuga ko abagenzi bakuwe muri ako kato mu bwato bahise berekeza mu modoka zari zibategereje.
Bazemererwa gusubira mu buzima bwabo busanzwe, ariko bazakomeza kubazwa amakuru mu minsi myinshi iri imbere hagenzurwa ubuzima bwabo, nkuko bitangazwa na minisiteri y'ubuzima mu Buyapani.
Abatagaragaweho iyo virusi ariko babanye mu gice kimwe n'abanduye muri ubwo bwato, bagomba kuguma mu bwato mu kindi gihe cy'inyongera cyo gushyirwa mu kato.
Abo bagenzi baturuka mu bihugu birenga 50, ari nayo mpamvu hari impungenge ko ubwo bwato bushobora kuba isoko nshyashya y'ubwandure bw'iyo virusi ku isi, nkuko uwo mugenzi wacu uri yo abivuga.
</doc>
<doc id='bbc_amakuru-51943931' type='mono' source_url='https://www.bbc.co.uk/gahuza/amakuru-51943931' term='COVID'>
Coronavirus ubu yageze muri leta 50 zose zigize Amerika
Icyorezo cya coronavirus ubu kimaze kugera muri leta zose 50 zigize Leta Zunze Ubumwe z'Amerika, nyuma yaho leta ya West Virginia ejo ku wa kabiri itangarije umuntu wa mbere wanduye iyo virusi.
Icyorezo cya coronavirus ubu kimaze kugera muri leta zose 50 zigize Leta Zunze Ubumwe z'Amerika, nyuma yaho leta ya West Virginia ejo ku wa kabiri itangarije umuntu wa mbere wanduye iyo virusi.
Ubwo yatangazaga uwo muntu wa mbere urwaye indwara y'ubuhumekero ya Covid-19 iterwa n'ubu bwoko bushya bwa coronavirus, Jim Justice, Guverineri w'iyo leta, yagize ati:
"Twari tubizi ko ibi biri hafi gushyika".
Ubuyobozi bw'umujyi wa New York City bwatangaje ko buri kwiga ku guhagarika ubuzima mu mujyi nk'uko byakozwe mu karere ka San Francisco Bay.
Kugeza ubu muri Amerika abantu 108 bamaze kwicwa n'iki cyorezo cya coronavirus naho abarenga 6,300 ni bo bamaze kwemezwa ko barwaye coronavirus muri iki gihugu.
Ku isi ubu habarurwa abantu hafi 200,000 bamaze kuyandura. Abagera hafi ku 8,000 imaze kubica.
Mu gihe ubutegetsi bwa Perezida Donald Trump buri gushaka amafaranga y'ingoboka ku bukungu angana na triyari imwe y'amadolari, umunyamabanga w'Amerika ushinzwe iby'imari hari ibyo yaburiye.
Amakuru avuga ko ejo ku wa kabiri nimugoroba, Steven Mnuchin yaburiye ukwabo abasenateri bo mu ishyaka ry'abarepubulikani ko inteko ishingamategeko ninanirwa kugira icyo ikoze, abadafite akazi muri Amerika bashobora kugera ku kigero cya 20%.
Icyo kigero cyaba cyenda gukuba inshuro ebyiri umubare w'abashomeri bari bariho mu gihe cy'ihungabana rikomeye ry'ubukungu ryabayeho muri Amerika mu mwaka wa 2008.
Bill de Blasio, umukuru w'umujyi wa New York City, yavuze ko mu minsi ibiri iri imbere azafata icyemezo niba yategeka ko abaturage miliyoni 8.5 "baguma iwabo".
Icyemezo nk'icyo ahanini cyatuma abantu batemererwa kuva mu ngo zabo, kikabemerera gukora ingendo za ngombwa bajya kugura imboga zo guteka cyangwa imiti, batembereza imbwa zabo cyangwa bakora imyitozo ngororangingo mu gihe cyose baba birinze guhura n'abandi bantu.
Bwana de Blasio yagize ati: "Ni icyemezo gikomeye cyane. Nta na rimwe mbere twigeze tuba mu bihe nk'ibi. Nta na rimwe nigeze numva ikintu nk'iki mu mateka y'umujyi wa New York City".
Abategetsi bo mu gace ka San Francisco Bay bamaze gutegeka abaturage miliyoni 6.7 bahatuye kuguma mu ngo zabo igihe cyose, ukuyemo aho bibaye ngombwa ko bava mu rugo, kugeza ku itariki ya 7 y'ukwezi gutaha kwa kane.
</doc>
