Minisiteri y'ubuzima mu Rwanda yatangaje ko hari abandi bantu bane(4) basanzemo Covid-19 mu Rwanda, aba bose ni Abanyarwanda kandi umwe muri bo ntaheruka kuva mu gihugu.
