Coronavirus: Abanyamahanga baherutse mu Bushinwa bagiye kubuzwa kwinjira muri Amerika
Leta Zunze Ubumwe z'Amerika zatangaje ibihe bidasanzwe mu rwego rw'ubuzima kubera coronavirus ikomeje gukwirakwira ndetse zivuga ko zizangira kuhinjira umunyamahanga wese wasuye Ubushinwa mu byumweru bibiri bishize.
Leta Zunze Ubumwe z'Amerika zatangaje ibihe bidasanzwe mu rwego rw'ubuzima kubera coronavirus ikomeje gukwirakwira ndetse zivuga ko zizangira kuhinjira umunyamahanga wese wasuye Ubushinwa mu byumweru bibiri bishize.
Alex Azar, umunyamabanga ushinzwe ubuzima w'Amerika, ejo ku wa gatanu yavuze ko Abanyamerika basubira mu gihugu cyabo bavuye mu ntara ya Hubei, aho iyo ndwara yatangiriye, bazashyirwa mu kato mu gihe cy'iminsi 14.
Bwana Azar yavuze ko izo ngamba nshya zizatangira gushyirwa mu bikorwa ejo ku cyumweru.
Yongeyeho ko ibyago byo kwandura coronavirus ku Banyamerika "bikiri hasi, kandi kubera izi ngamba nshya n'izabanje, turi gukora kuburyo ibyago [byo kwandura] bikomeza kuba hasi".
Abantu barenga 11,000 ni bo bamaze kwemezwa ko banduye ubu bwoko bushya bw'iyi virusi - benshi muri bo bakaba ari abo mu Bushinwa - kuva iyo virusi yagaragara bwa mbere mu kwezi kwa cumi na kabiri.
Abantu barenga 100 bamaze gutangazwa ko banduye iyo virusi hanze y'Ubushinwa, mu bihugu 22.
Ejo ku wa gatanu, Ubushinwa bwatangaje ko umubare w'abamaze guhitanwa na coronavirus bageze kuri 259 - barimo 249 bo mu ntara ya Hubei.
Mbere yaho, byagaragaye ko umubare w'abantu bashya banduye coronavirus umaze kurenga uw'abanduye icyorezo cya Sars, cyageze mu bihugu bibarirwa muri za mirongo ku isi mu mwaka wa 2003.
Icyo gihe abantu barenga 8,100 banduye Sars - indwara ishegesha bikomeye imyamya y'ubuhumekero - mu gihe cy'amezi umunani yamaze. Bose hamwe, abantu 774 ni bo bishwe na Sars.
Ku wa kane w'iki cyumweru, ishami ry'umuryango w'abibumbye ryita ku buzima (OMS/WHO) ryatangaje ko isi iri mu bihe bidasanzwe kubera ubu bwoko bushya bwa coronavirus.
