Ntute umwanya ngo:
Muri ivyo vyose nta na kimwe gifasha kuzibira uwo mugera.
Nta kintu na kimwe cerekana ko imbwa canke akayabu  gashobora kwandura uwo mugera.
Hagati aho, ivyo ntibivuga ko utokwama ukaraba n'isabuni mu gihe wabikorakoye.
Uwo mugera mushasha wa coronavirus uzwi ko wavuye mw'isoko rigurisha ibitungwa i Wuhan, mu Bushinwa - arico gituma uvugwa ko wavuye mu bikoko.
Uwo mugera ushobora kuba utashotse uboneka mu bikoko imbere y'uko usimba ukandukira abantu, kandi ni ko n'iyindi migera itangura, nk'akarorero ibicurane, Ebola, SARS.
Ariko ivyo ntibivuga ko ibikoko muri rusangi biteye ubwoba canke ko ari vyo bikwiragiza uwo mugera.
Abantu nka bose batangura kwerekana ibimenyetso bisanzwe (inkorora, ubushuhe) kandi barakira.
Hagati aho, uwo mugera urashobora gutuma abantu bamwe bamwe basinzikara (bagafatwa n'imisonga, canke bakagira ingorane zo guhema), ariko abahitanwa nawo usanga ari bake (kubera bagize ingorane zikomeye z'amahaha) mu Bushinwa.
Ntiwibagire kandi ko hari indwara y'ibicurane igihe cose mu rushana (mu gihe c'imvura), kandi vyica abantu - mu Bwongereza, abantu bashika 600 bama bahitanwa n'ibicurane buri mwaka.
Nko mu Bwongereza, kubera ingingo nyinshi zafashwe, hari igihamana kibi co gufatwa n'ibicurane gusumba coronavirus.
Hanyuma kandi, ingingo yo gushira ukwabo abantu bose bavuye i Wuhan ituma uwo mugera utagira ingaruka mbi.
Igisabwa ubu muri ico gihugu, ni uko abantu bokwicandagisha ibicurane muri kino gihe.
