Abanyeshuri babarirwa mu bihumbi bo mu Rwanda bigaga mu mujyi wa Goma muri DR Congo babujijwe kujyayo kuko Ebola yahageze mu mezi abiri ashize, ubu 426 bagiye gutangira kwigishwa  mu Rwanda.
Abanyeshuri babarirwa mu bihumbi bo mu Rwanda bigaga mu mujyi wa Goma muri DR Congo babujijwe kujyayo kuko Ebola yahageze mu mezi abiri ashize, ubu 426 bagiye gutangira kwigishwa  mu Rwanda.
Isaac Munyakazi, umunyamabanga wa Leta ushinzwe amashuri y'incuke, abanza n'ayisumbuye uyu munsi yasuye ikigo bagiye gutangira kwigishirizwamo icyongereza bitegura kuzigira mu Rwanda.
Bwana Munyakazi avuga ko abo bagiye gutegurwa bakazatangirana n'abandi umwaka w'amashuri mu Rwanda mu kwezi kwa mbere.
Bamwe mu babyeyi b'aba banyeshuri baganiriye na BBC mu cyumweru gishize bavuze ko nubwo amashuri yabo yaboneka mu Rwanda, ubushobozi bwo kuyishyura batabufite.
Aba babyeyi bagaragaza ko amashuri hakurya i Goma, aho bigisha mu gifaransa, babasha kuyishyura mu bushobozi bwabo mu gihe ayo mu Rwanda kuri bo ahenze.
Umwe mu babyeyi witwa Ézéchiel Rwibasira yavuze ko bakurikirana amakuru bakumva ko muri DR Congo Ebola isa n'itagihari.
