Rwanda: Dr Diane Gashumba, uwa gatatu weguye ku buminisitiri mu gihe cy'iminsi 7
Dr Diane Gashumba wari Minisitiri w'ubuzima mu Rwanda yaraye yeguye ku mirimo ye, nkuko bitangazwa n'ibiro bya minisitiri w'intebe.
Dr Diane Gashumba wari Minisitiri w'ubuzima mu Rwanda yaraye yeguye ku mirimo ye, nkuko bitangazwa n'ibiro bya minisitiri w'intebe.
Kwegura kwe "kuje gukurikira amakosa akomeye n'imiyoborere idakwiye yakomeje kugaragaza", nkuko bikubiye mu butumwa bwo kuri Twitter bw'ibiro bya minisitiri w'intebe w'u Rwanda.
Nta bindi bisobanuro byatanzwe ku kwegura kwe.
Dr Gashumba yari Minisitiri w'ubuzima guhera mu kwezi kwa cumi mu 2016 - umwanya yagezeho asimbuye Dr Agnes Binagwaho wayoboye iyo minisiteri kuva mu 2011 akayivamo yirukanwe.
Mu byo Dr Gashumba yagizemo uruhare mu gihe cy'imyaka irenga itatu ku buyobozi, harimo n'ibikorwa byo gukumira ko indwara ya Ebola muri Repubulika ya Demokarasi ya Kongo igera mu Rwanda.
Kwegura kwe kuje gukurikira ukwa Evode Uwizeyimana wari umunyamabanga wa leta muri minisiteri y'ubutabera na Isaac Munyakazi wari umunyamabanga ushinzwe amashuri abanza n'ayisumbuye, batangajwe ko beguye ku wa gatanu ushize.
</doc>
<doc id='bbc_141021_afurikayepfo' type='mono' source_url='http://www.bbc.co.uk/gahuza/amakuru/2014/10/141021_afurikayepfo' term='ebola'>
Afurika yepfo ntizakira imikino y'igikombe cya Afurika
Ministiri ushinzwe imikino muri Afurika yepfo - Fikile Mbalula - yavuze ko igihugu cye kidashobora gusimbura Maroc mu kwakira imikino ya nyuma y'igikombe cya Afurika cy'ibihugu iteganijwe mu kwezi kwa mbere k'umwaka utaha.
Ministiri ushinzwe imikino muri Afurika yepfo - Fikile Mbalula - yavuze ko igihugu cye kidashobora gusimbura Maroc mu kwakira imikino ya nyuma y'igikombe cya Afurika cy'ibihugu iteganijwe mu kwezi kwa mbere k'umwaka utaha.
Yagize ati: "ingengo y'imali yacu uko imeze ubungubu ntabwo yatuma tubikora, ntibishoboka."
Impuzahamashyirahamwe y'umupira w'amaguru muri Afurika - CAF - yari yasabye Afurika yepfo niba yeteguye kwakira iyo mikino igihugu cya Maroc kiramutse kitayakiriye nkuko biteganijwe.
Maroc yasabye CAF guhindura amatariki iyo mikino igomba kuberaho kubera gutinya ko Ebola yinjira ku butaka bwayo.
Afurika yepfo ni kimwe mu bihugu birindwi CAF yasabye kuba byasimbura Maroc itishimiye kwakira iyo mikino hagati y'itariki ya 17 z'ukwa mbere 2015 kugeza ku ya 8 z'ukwa kabiri.
Indwara ya Ebola imaze guhitana abantu barenga 4500 biganje cyane cyane muri Afurika y'uburengerazuba.
