Abashinzwe ubuzima mu burasirazuba bwa DR Congo baratangaza ko abantu 1,000 bavuwe bagakira indwara ya Ebola bakava mu bigo bavurirwagamo bagataha.
Abashinzwe ubuzima mu burasirazuba bwa DR Congo baratangaza ko abantu 1,000 bavuwe bagakira indwara ya Ebola bakava mu bigo bavurirwagamo bagataha.
