Ibihugu bikikije DR Congo mu burasirazuba birimo u Burundi n'u Rwanda byafashe ingamba zikomeye zo gukumira iki cyorezo ngo ntikirenge umupaka.
U Rwanda rwahagaritse abanyeshuri bigaga mu mujyi wa Goma bataha mu Rwanda buri munsi, kugeza ubu ntibarongera kwemrerwa gusubirayo nubwo ho batangiye amasomo mu kwezi gushize.
David Gressly avuga ko nubwo Ebola yagabanutse cyane ariko urugamba bariho rutararangira, gusa ko ubu hari uburyo bufite bukomeye bwo kuyirwanya.
Ubu nibwo Ebola yageze henshi kandi igatinda muri DR Congo, ubu ariko ni nabwo hari urukingo rwayo abahanga bavuga ko rukora ku gipimo cya 97%, umuryango w'abibumbye uvuga ko rwarengeye abantu 226,000.
</doc>
<doc id='bbc_amakuru-45431313' type='mono' source_url='https://www.bbc.co.uk/gahuza/amakuru-45431313' term='ebola'>
"Ebola yageze" mu mujyi wa Butembo ukorerwamo ubucuruzi buhinda muri Kongo
Minsiteri y'ubuzima muri Repubulika ya Demokarasi ya Kongo yabwiye ibiro ntaramakuru Reuters ko Ebola yageze mu mujyi wa Butembo ukorerwamo ubucuruzi buhinda mu ntara ya Kivu y'amajyaruguru mu burasirazuba bw'iki gihugu.
Minsiteri y'ubuzima muri Repubulika ya Demokarasi ya Kongo yabwiye ibiro ntaramakuru Reuters ko Ebola yageze mu mujyi wa Butembo ukorerwamo ubucuruzi buhinda mu ntara ya Kivu y'amajyaruguru mu burasirazuba bw'iki gihugu.
Umujyi wa Butembo utuwe n'abaturage bagera hafi ku bihumbi 900, ukaba unakorana ubucuruzi n'igihugu gituranyi cya Uganda.
Ibiro ntaramakuru Reuters byasubiyemo amagambo y'umuyobozi w'uyu mujyi Sylvain Kanyamanda agira ati:
"Turasaba abaturage kuba maso kandi bakubahiriza amabwiriza yose y'isuku nkuko atangwa n'abaganga."
Kuva mu kwezi kwa karindwi, Ebola imaze guhitana abantu bagera kuri 80 muri Kongo naho abandi 40 barayanduye.
Benshi mu bishwe na Ebola bari batuye mu bice by'icyaro ariko nanone hari abagiye batangazwa ko bayirwaye  mu duce tw'umujyi, nko mu mujyi wa Beni.
Iyi ni inshuro ya 10 Ebola yadutse muri Kongo kuva yagaragara bwa mbere mu majyaruguru y'iki gihugu mu mwaka wa 1976.
