<doc id='bbc_amakuru-48891671' type='mono' source_url='https://www.bbc.co.uk/gahuza/amakuru-48891671' term='ebola'>
Sudani y'Epfo ivuga ko yongereye ibikorwa byo gupima Ebola ku mupaka na Kongo
Umutegetsi wo muri minisiteri y'ubuzima muri Sudani y'Epfo avuga ko iki gihugu cyongereye ibikorwa byo gupima indwara ya Ebola ku mupaka gihana na Repubulika ya Demokarasi ya Kongo.
Umutegetsi wo muri minisiteri y'ubuzima muri Sudani y'Epfo avuga ko iki gihugu cyongereye ibikorwa byo gupima indwara ya Ebola ku mupaka gihana na Repubulika ya Demokarasi ya Kongo.
Ni nyuma yaho muri iki cyumweru umuntu asanganwe iyo ndwara muri Kongo kuri kilometero 70 uvuye muri Sudani y'Epfo.
Dr Richard Lino Laku yabwiye Radio Miraya yo muri Sudani y'Epfo ko iki gihugu cyohereje muri leta ya Yei River itsinda rivuye mu murwa mukuru Juba ryo gufasha abasanzwe bakora mu rwego rw'ubuzima muri ako karere.
Yongeyeho ko bakomeje kugenzura niba haba hari abaturage banyuze "mu nzira zitemewe n'amategeko" binjira muri Sudani y'Epfo bavuye muri Kongo, aho abantu barenga 2300 bamaze kwandura Ebola mu mezi 11 ashize.
Amakuru avuga ko uwo muntu wasanganywe Ebola ari kuri kilometero 70 uvuye ku mupaka wa Sudani y'Epfo ari umugore w'imyaka 40 y'amavuko wakoze urugendo rwa kilometero 500 ava i Beni mu ntara ya Kivu y'amajyaruguru.
Ishami ry'umuryango w'abibumbye ryita ku buzima (OMS) rivuga ko iyi Ebola yo muri Kongo - ihadutse ku nshuro ya 10 - imaze guhitana abarenga 1500.
OMS ivuga ko "mu gihugu no mu karere ibyago byo kuyandura bikiri hejuru cyane", ariko iyi Ebola ntabwo iritwa ikibazo giteje akaga amahanga.
Mu kwezi gushize kwa gatandatu, muri Uganda abantu babiri bari baherutse kujya muri Kongo bapfuye bazize Ebola, ariko kuva icyo gihe nta bandi bantu baratangazwa ko banduye Ebola bo hanze ya Kongo.
</doc>
<doc id='bbc_amakuru-50282281' type='mono' source_url='https://www.bbc.co.uk/gahuza/amakuru-50282281' term='ebola'>
DR Congo:Umunyamakuru wakoraga ibiganiro kuri Ebola yishwe
Umunyamakuru w'umushyushyarugamba ('animateur') wakoreraga radio y'abaturage yo mu burasirazuba bwa Repubulika ya Demokarasi ya Kongo atanga ubutumwa bwo kurwanya Ebola, yishwe mu ijoro ry'ejo ku wa gatandatu rishyira none ku cyumweru.
Umunyamakuru w'umushyushyarugamba ('animateur') wakoreraga radio y'abaturage yo mu burasirazuba bwa Repubulika ya Demokarasi ya Kongo atanga ubutumwa bwo kurwanya Ebola, yishwe mu ijoro ry'ejo ku wa gatandatu rishyira none ku cyumweru.
Mu gihe cy'umwaka ushize, habaye ibitero bibarirwa muri za mirongo ku bigo nderabuzima no ku bantu bakora mu bikorwa by'ubutabazi bwo kurwanya Ebola.
Byibazwa ko urwo rugomo rutizwa umurindi n'imyumvire y'amakenga y'abaturage bamwe na n'ubu bacyemeza ko virusi ya Ebola itabaho, nubwo imaze guhitana abarenga 2,100 muri iki gihugu.
Abantu bitwaje imbunda n'imihoro bacyekwa kuba ari inyeshyamba za Mai-Mai bagabye igitero ku rugo rw'uwo munyamakuru ruri i Lwemba mu ijoro ryakeye.
Ibitangazamakuru byo muri DR Congo bivuga ko Papy Mumbere Mahamba yishwe, umugore we afatwa ku ngufu n'inzu ye iratwikwa.
Uwo munyamakuru yari amaze gutangaza ikiganiro kuri radio y'abaturage akora ubukangurambaga bwo kurwanya icyorezo cya Ebola.
Bishoboka ko iyicwa rye ryaturutse ku myumvire ya bamwe yashinze imizi, bashidikanya niba koko Ebola ibaho ndetse batizera abakora mu bikorwa by'ubutabazi bwo kubuza Ebola gukomeza gukwirakwira.
Mu mwaka ushize, habaye ibitero bigera hafi kuri magana abiri ku bakozi bo mu bikorwa by'ubuzima, ku modoka z'imbangukiragutabara ('ambulances') no ku bigo nderabuzima.
Ibyo byakomye mu nkokora ibikorwa by'ubutabazi byo guhagarika Ebola.
</doc>
