<doc id='bbc_amakuru-49328120' type='mono' source_url='https://www.bbc.co.uk/gahuza/amakuru-49328120' term='ebola'>
Ubushakashatsi bwagaragaje ko imiti ibiri mishya ya Ebola 'iyikiza ku kigero cya 90%'
Mu gihe cya vuba kiri imbere, Ebola ishobora kuba igiye kuba indwara "ishobora kwirindwa kandi ikavurwa igakira" nyuma yaho igerageza ry'imiti ibiri rigaragaje gutanga ikigero giteye imbere cyo gukira, nkuko bivugwa n'abahanga muri siyansi.
Mu gihe cya vuba kiri imbere, Ebola ishobora kuba igiye kuba indwara "ishobora kwirindwa kandi ikavurwa igakira" nyuma yaho igerageza ry'imiti ibiri rigaragaje gutanga ikigero giteye imbere cyo gukira, nkuko bivugwa n'abahanga muri siyansi.
Imiti ine yageragerejwe ku barwayi ba Ebola barenga 700 muri Repubulika ya Demokarasi ya Kongo, ahagaragara iyi ndwara muri iki gihe.
Ibizamini by'ibanze bizwi kuri ubu ni iby'abarwayi 499 ba mbere muri abo.
Imiti ibiri muri iyo yagaragaje guhangana na Ebola ku kigero cyo hejuru, nkuko ubu bushakashatsi bwabigaragaje.
Abategetsi bo mu rwego rw'ubuzima bavuga ko ubu iyi miti igiye gukoreshwa mu kuvura abarwayi bose ba Ebola muri Kongo.
Ikigo cy'Amerika kiga ku ndwara zandura ndetse n'ingaruka y'imiti - cyitwa NIAID mu magambo ahinnye y'Icyongereza - ni kimwe mu bateye inkunga igerageza ry'iyo miti.
Cyatangaje ko ibyavuye muri iryo gerageza ari "inkuru nziza cyane" mu rugamba rwo kurwanya Ebola.
Ubu bushakashatsi bwakozwe n'ikigo mpuzamahanga cy'ubushakashatsi, buyoborwa n'ishami ry'umuryango w'abibumbye ryita ku buzima (OMS). Bwatangiye mu kwezi kwa cumi na kumwe k'umwaka ushize.
Iyi miti izwi nka REGN-EB3 na mAb114, irwanya virusi ya Ebola mu maraso, ikayica intege mu turemangingo tw'umubiri.
Dr Anthony Fauci, umukuru w'ikigo NIAID, yavuze ko iyi ari "imiti ya mbere, mu bushakashatsi bwa siyansi bukomeye, yagaragaje mu buryo bugaragara kugabanya ubukana bwo kwica" bwa Ebola ku barwayi.
Iyi miti ya REGN-EB3 na mAb114 yakozwe hashingiwe ku bigize amaraso y'abarokotse Ebola - indwara imaze guhitana abantu barenga 1800 muri Kongo guhera mu kwa munani k'umwaka ushize.
Indi miti ibiri, yitwa ZMapp na Remdesivir, yakuwe mu igerageza kuko basanze itanga umusaruro mucye.
Sabue Mulangu, umushakashatsi ku ndwara zandura wagize uruhare muri iri gerageza, yavuze ko ibyarivuyemo bivuze ko abategetsi bo mu rwego rw'ubuzima bashobora "gushimangira babwira rubanda ko abarenga 90% bakira" Ebola iyo bavuwe hakiri kare.
Ashima ibyavuye muri ubwo bushakashatsi,  Jeremy Farrar uyobora ikigo Wellcome Trust cyo mu Bwongereza gikora ubushakashatsi mu by'ubuzima, yavuze ko "nta shiti ko iyo miti izarokora ubuzima bw'abantu".
Bwana Farrar yavuze ko ibyavuye muri ubwo bushakashatsi bigaragaza ko abahanga muri siyansi bari hafi guhindura Ebola indwara "ishobora kwirindwa no kuvurwa igakira".
Ariko yongeyeho ko uburyo bwiza cyane kurusha ubundi bwose bwo guhangana na Ebola ari "urukingo rwiza".
Bwana Farrar avuga ko urukingo ari ubwoko bw'umuti uvugurura ubwirinzi bw'umubiri ku ndwara.
</doc>
<doc id='bbc_151229_guinee_ebola' type='mono' source_url='http://www.bbc.co.uk/gahuza/amakuru/2015/12/151229_guinee_ebola' term='ebola'>
Nta mugera wa Ebola ukirangwa muri Guinee
Ishami rya Onu rishinzwe amagara y’abantu kw’isi, OMS, vyitezwe ko ritangaza uyu musi ko igihugu ca Guinee kitakirangwamwo ingwara yandukira ya Ebola.
Ishami rya Onu rishinzwe amagara y’abantu kw’isi, OMS, vyitezwe ko ritangaza uyu musi ko igihugu ca Guinee kitakirangwamwo ingwara yandukira ya Ebola.
Ingwara ya Ebola yadutse muri ico gihugu mu myaka ibiri iheze.
Iyo ngwara ya Ebola yahitanye abantu benshi mu bihugu biri mu burengero bwa Afrika, na cane cane ibihugu vya Guinne, Liberia na Sierra Leone.
Abanye Guinee bariko baritegira kwigina ituzwa ry’iyo ngwara mu munezero.
Benshi bavuga ko batanguye intango nshasha n’umwaka mushasha kuri prezida wabo Alpha Conde, ikiringo ciwe gishasha catanguye mu ndwi iheze.
Ariko uwo mugera wa Ebola ubasize aho umwansi ashaka na cane cane mu mibano no mu butunzi.
Ishiirahamwe mpuzamakungu rifasha ibibondo UNICEF, rivuga ko muri ico gihugu abana 6,220 bahevye ishure, kubera kubura umuvyeyi umwe canke bose ko ari babiri bazize iyo ngwara.
Wengi wanasema wanaanza mwanzo mpya na mwaka mpya na pia kwa rais wao Alpha Conde ambaye muhula wake wa uongozi ulianza wiki iliyopita.
Hata hivyo ugonjwa wa Ebola umeweka kumbukumbu mbaya nchini humo, hususan athari za kijamii na kiuchumi.
Abakize iyo ngwara na bo, babayeho nabi kandi barabinuba cane.
</doc>
