Abasirikare bane ba ONU baturuka muri Malawi bishwe muri Congo
Igisirikare ca Malawi camenyesheje ko bane mu basirikare baco bafasha gukomeza amahoro muri Repubulika y'Intwaro rusangi ya Congo mu mugwi Monusco wa ONU bishwe n'inyeshamba.
Igisirikare ca Malawi camenyesheje ko bane mu basirikare baco bafasha gukomeza amahoro muri Repubulika y'Intwaro rusangi ya Congo mu mugwi Monusco wa ONU bishwe n'inyeshamba.
Umuvugizi w'ico gisirikare yavuze ko abo basirikare baguye mu mutego ku munsi wa gatatu bari mu bikorwa vya gisirikare hamwe na bagenzi babo baturuka muri Afrika Yepfo na Tanzaniya.
Yavuze ko hari abandi basirikare bakomeretse bariko baravugwa.
Uwo muvugizi w'igisirikare yavuze ko batazi umugwi w'inyeshamba wagavye ico gitero uwariwo.
Imigwi myinshi irimwo uwitwa "Allied Democratic Forces" (ADF) ugizwe n'abagwanyi b'abaganda, irakorera cane muri ico gihugu.
ONU iramaze kugabisha ivuga ko ingwano yiyongeye muri ico gihugu, ko ubwicanyi buhari hamwe n'ikiza ca Ebola bishobora kuburagiza amatora ategekanywa mu kwezi kuza.
Mu kwezi kw'icumi mu 2017, abasirikare 14 baturuka mu gihugu ca Tanzaniya barishwe mu gitero cagabwe mu buseruko bw'ico gihugu ca Congo.
Ico gihe imwe mu maradiyo akorana na ONU ikaba yavuze ko umugwi ADF ariwo wagavye ico gitero.
</doc>
<doc id='bbc_141127_ebolavaccines' type='mono' source_url='http://www.bbc.co.uk/gahuza/amakuru/2014/11/141127_ebolavaccines' term='ebola'>
Ebola : Inkingo za Ebola mu mwaka utaha
Umukuru w'umuryango ufasha mu gukora ubushakashatsi yavuze ko amasosiyete 3 akomeye yiyemeje gukora inkingo za Ebola zigera ku mamiliyoni mu mwaka utaha.
Umukuru w'umuryango ufasha mu gukora ubushakashatsi yavuze ko amasosiyete 3 akomeye yiyemeje gukora inkingo za Ebola zigera ku mamiliyoni mu mwaka utaha.
GSK, Johnson and Johnson na Merck, buri sosiyete yose izakora urukingo rwayo.
Hari ibimenyetso bigaragaza ko urukingo rwa GSK arirwo rwiza nyuma yaho rugaragarije ko rwafashije kurinda imibiri y'abantu 20 bakoreweho isuzumwa.
Ariko hari irindi geragezwa rizaba. Professor Jeremy Farrar ukuriye umuryango ufasha Wellcome Trust, yavuze ko afite ibyiringiro byuko abantu babarirwa mu bihumbi barimo n'abakozi bo kwa muganga bazabona urwo rukingo mubyo yise "urwego rwa kabiri rw'ubushakashatsi".
Hagati aho abakorera imiryango ifasha mu majyepfo y'uburasirazuba bwa Guinea baravuga ko imibare y'abarwayi ba Ebola ikomeje kwiyongera mu gace yatangiriyemo kandi ko nta byangombwa bihagije bafite byo kuyihashya.
MSF na Red Cross ishami ryo mu Bufaransa baravuga ko barengewe n'umubare w'abarwayi wakomeje kwiyongera muri ibi byumweru bishize.
Ngo nubwo hari ibigo bishya bishyirwaho, birahita byuzura abarwayi mu minsi mike.
Umuryango mpuzamahanga wita k'ubuzima, PAM, uravuga ko muri rusange imibare y'abarwayi ba Ebola muri Guinea itiyongera ariko muri Sierra Leone ariho babona abarwayi bashya benshi.
</doc>
