<doc id='bbc_150116_afcon2015_ebola' type='mono' source_url='http://www.bbc.co.uk/gahuza/amakuru/2015/01/150116_afcon2015_ebola' term='ebola'>
Ebola yahungabanije ite CAF 2015?
Kugeza ku itariki ya 12 z'uku kwezi kwa mbere Ebola imaze guhitana abantu 8,386 mu bihugu 6 hashingiwe ku mibare itangwa n'ishami ry'umuryango w'abibumbye ryita ku buzima.
Kugeza ku itariki ya 12 z'uku kwezi kwa mbere Ebola imaze guhitana abantu 8,386 mu bihugu 6 hashingiwe ku mibare itangwa n'ishami ry'umuryango w'abibumbye ryita ku buzima.
Cyakora, iki cyago ntikiragaragara muri iki gihugu ndetse Guvernoma ikaba yarafashe ingamba zikomeye zo kugikumira zirimo no kwiyambaza impuguke z'abaganga zivuye mu gihugu cya Cuba.
Buri mukinyi ndetse n'undi munyamahanga wese winjiye muri Guinnee Equatorial agomba kubanza gupimwa Ebola.
Julia Nchama Abeso Ayomo, umukozi wo mu biro bihagarariye iki gihugu i Londres yatangaje ko buri muntu wese winjira muri Guinee Equatorial agomba kubanza gukorerwa ibizamini mu rwego rwo gukumira iki cyorezo.
Ibihugu bya Guinnea, Sierra Leone na Liberia ni byo byashegeshwe na Ebola.
Muri ibi bihugu Guinnea ni yo yashoboye kubona itiki kandi kubigeraho ni ikintu gikomeye urebye inzira yanyuze.
Nta mukino n'umwe wo gushaka itiki iki gihugu cyakiriye kandi abakinyi bahungabanijwe bikomeye n'iki cyorezo.
Ibrahima Traore ukinira ikipe ya Borussia Monchengladbach yavuze ko abakinnyi ba Guinnea bap imwe Ebola bari mu rwambariro mbere gato y'umukino ukomeye wabahuje na Togo.
Avugana na BBC,Traore yagize ati: "Twabibonyemo agasuzuguro. Twabonye ko mu bindi bihugu hari ababona twe Abanga Guinnea nk'aho tutari ibiremwamuntu, batubonaga nk'indwara ubwayo".
"Ibi byose tugomba kubyibagirwa kugira ngo dushobore kwitwara neza muri Guinnee Equatorial. Ni ngombwa ko tubikorera igihugu cyacu ndetse n'abandi bantu bose bakozweho n'iyi ndwara"
"Tugomba kwereka buri wese isura nziza ya Guinea":
"Twahawe amadolari 30,000 nk'ishimwe ry'uko twashoboye kubona itiki. Aya yose nahise nyaha imiryango y'ubutabazi ifasha mu guhashya iki cyorezo. Muri iyi mikino y'igikombe cy'Africa tugomba guhatana twumva ko turwanira abaturage bose bugarijwe na Ebola"
</doc>
<doc id='bbc_amakuru-46169098' type='mono' source_url='https://www.bbc.co.uk/gahuza/amakuru-46169098' term='ebola'>
Abarenga 200 nibo bamaze guhitanwa na Ebola muri Congo
Abantu barenga 200 nibo bamaze gupfa bahitanywe n'ikiza ca Ebola muri Repubulika ya Demokarasi ya Congo, nkuko abo mu gisata c'amagara y'abantu babishikiriza.
Abantu barenga 200 nibo bamaze gupfa bahitanywe n'ikiza ca Ebola muri Repubulika ya Demokarasi ya Congo, nkuko abo mu gisata c'amagara y'abantu babishikiriza.
Igice c'abapfuye n'abo mu gisagara ca Beni kiri mu ntara ya Kivu y'uburaruko kibamwo abanyagihugu 800000, nkuko ubutegetsi bw'igihugu bw'amagara y'abantu buvuga.
Mw'isekeza ryo gucandaga, abanyagihugu 25000 nibo bamaze kuronka urucanco.
Umushikiranganji w'amagara y'abantu Oly Ilunga yavuze ko inyeshamba zitwaje ibigwanisho ziguma ziburagiza imigwi y'abavuzi.
Mu kwezi kw'icenda, ibikogwa vyo gucandaga vyarahagaritswe vy'agateganyo, igihe umugwi w'inyeshamba ugabiye igitero camaze amasaha menshi.
Igihugu ca Congo kimaze imyaka myinshi kirangwamwo ingwano n'indyane za politike.
Ikiza ca Ebola cadutse mu kwezi kw'indwi kigira ic'icumi cibasiye igihugu kuva mu 1976.
Uwo mugera umuntu yandura aruko atarukiweko n'amama avuye ku mubiri w'umuntu awusanganywe, urashobora kwica.
Mu cegeranyo giheruka gusohogwa n'ubushikiranganji bw'amagara y'abantu, bivugwa ko hari abantu 291 bamaze kuwandura, 201 bakaba bamaze kwitaba Imana.
Umugwi w'inteko za Onu zifasha gucungera amahoro n'umutekano muri Congo, usaba imigwi y'abagwanyi kutaburagiza ibikogwa vy'abavuzi bagwanya ico kiza.
Bwana Ilunga yavuze ku munsi wa gatanu ko imigwi y'abavuzi yama yagabweko ibitero, igakubagugwa, ibikoresho vy'akazi bikononwa, abavuzi bakanyuruzwa.
"Babiri bo mu mugwi wacu wo gutabara abasinzikaye barishwe muri ivyo bitero," niko yabandanije avuga.
Mu ndwi iheze, umuyobozi mukuru w'igisata ca Onu citaho amagara y'abantu "Organisation Mondiale pour la Santé", Tedros Adhanom Ghebreyesus, yavuze ko ikibazo c'umutekano kiri mu bibujije kugwanya neza ico kiza.
</doc>
