Sierra Leone: Jimmy Thoronka ashobora kwirukanwa
Umwe mu banonozi bo muri Sierra Leone wabuze igihe yari mwirushanwa rya Commonwealth ryaberaga muri Scotland umwaka ushize ashobora kwirukanwa mu Bwongereza nyuma yaho asangiwe aba mu muhanda.
